data.description:
Permanently affixed manufactured home. Beautiful and rare 4 bedroom/ 3 bathroom find on a 1.24-acre pristine, private land.  Inside you will find a beautiful stone fireplace, an extra-large kitchen with an island, range, dishwasher and laminate wood flooring and tile with custom paint throughout. Nice exterior with covered front and rear patio and space for your toys with room to roam. On the back of the home there are 2 studios that may be used as office or guest room.

Disclosures: Manufactured home, Property uses a well shared among 3 properties, Property uses a septic system.
